casebody.data:
Michael RINALDI, petitioner,
v.
Donna ZICKEFOOSE, Warden. No. 13-5972. Supreme Court of the United States Oct. 15, 2013. Case below, 532 Fed.Appx. ----. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit denied. Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this petition.
